 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Mon, 26 Apr 2010 20:11:37 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.8.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll_fstab_generator: unref udev_device structures.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Sun, 25 Apr 2010 13:21:28 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.8.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll_fstab_generator: rename gengetopt generated filename from
    cmdline.[ch] to fll_fstab_cmdline.[ch].
  * fll-fstab: remove reference to workaround.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Fri, 23 Apr 2010 21:40:19 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.8.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll_fstab_generator: add -b --blkid option to use libblkid to probde
    for filesystem type.
  * fll_fstab_generator: fold mountpoint detection function into
    process_disk().
  * fll_fstab_generator: do not rely on DM_NAME udev property to
    identify devmapper devices.
  * fll_fstab_generator: enumerate for DEVTYPE disk or partition, do not
    explicitly set a match for DEVNAME /dev/mapper/*, they are DEVTYPE
    disk.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Fri, 23 Apr 2010 00:15:58 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.8.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll_fstab_generator: port to C program which uses libudev to
    enumerate block devices.
    - build-depend on gengetopt, pkg-config and libudev-dev
    - fll-live-utils is now arch: any
  * fll_resume_validate: removed.
  * fll-fstab: s/swapless/noswap/;s/nomnt/nomounts/.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Thu, 22 Apr 2010 20:01:18 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll-reboot: mark as interactive.
  * fll-reboot: remove everything which umountfs takes care of.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Thu, 15 Apr 2010 22:47:39 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll-reboot: do not provide reboot & halt, adjust dependencies to
    sequence script after unountfs but before umountroot, halt and
    reboot. Do not override halt/reboot lsb info.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Thu, 15 Apr 2010 22:36:02 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * add umountfs and umountroot to X-Stop-After of fll-reboot, thanks to kelmo.

 -- Stefan Lippers-Hollmann <s.l-h@gmx.de>  Thu, 15 Apr 2010 02:17:14 +0200

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.4) unstable; urgency=low

  * Drop invalid dependencies of perl,libfile-slurp-perl for fll-live-
    utils and shlibs for fll-live-xorgconfig.
  * Fix fll-live-initscripts.postrm.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Thu, 15 Apr 2010 07:30:44 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll-reboot: don't provide/ override umountfs/ umountroot for now, it breaks
    lvm2.

 -- Stefan Lippers-Hollmann <s.l-h@gmx.de>  Wed, 14 Apr 2010 19:49:36 +0200

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll-live-initscripts: do not create template /etc/default/fll-init
    /etc/default/fll-locales. Do not remove /etc/default/fll-init, its
    now not created.
  * fll-reboot: declare a X-Stop-After dependency to fix startpar
    makefile style shutdown. This is a fragile workaround which is
    required due to our replacing of umountroot/halt/reboot scripts.
  * fll-reboot: provide and override umountfs/umountroot.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Wed, 14 Apr 2010 23:48:51 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Remove all ucf crap, it is unused until now.
  * insserv is now pseudo-essential so do not special case it.
  * fll-init: touch /fastboot to avoid checkfs/checkroot while allowing
    those services to be present. Installer will need to undo this.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Wed, 14 Apr 2010 22:31:39 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.7.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Remove common functions insert_initscript()/remove_initscript() and any
    traces of code which used them.
  * Remove fll_analyze_initscripts, no longer used.
  * fll-init: drop code which loaded capability module.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Wed, 14 Apr 2010 21:27:18 +1000

fll-live-initscripts (3.6.26) unstable; urgency=low

  * drop depends on $remote_fs from fll-locales, to break dependency circle,
    this is broken and needs large scale fixes.

 -- Stefan Lippers-Hollmann <s.l-h@gmx.de>  Wed, 10 Mar 2010 23:26:46 +0100

fll-live-initscripts (3.6.25) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Nikolas Poniros ]
  * Added lxdm to distro-defaults to create/remove needed insserv overrides

  [ Stefan Lippers-Hollmann ]
  * drop build-depends on dash, it's now essential. Thanks to edhunter.
  * bump standards version to 3.8.4, no changes necessary.
  * switch to dpkg-source 3.0 (native) format.
  * fix lintian warnings:
    - init.d-script-sourcing-without-test, by replacing unrecognized -s checks
      with -r.
    - init.d-script-missing-dependency-on-remote_fs, while (guaranteed) not an
      issue in our environment, this is correct.
    - fll_xorgconfig.8: spelling-error-in-manpage s/seperated/separated/.
    - fll-reboot: init.d-script-does-not-provide-itself
    - locales: script-not-executable
  * re-indent locales.
  * update and harmonize debian/copyright.

 -- Stefan Lippers-Hollmann <s.l-h@gmx.de>  Wed, 10 Mar 2010 03:09:14 +0100

