fll-live-initscripts (3.5.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * update shipped PCI IDs in contrib:
    - xserver-xorg-video-ati 1:6.12.2-2
    - xserver-xorg-video-nv 1:2.1.13-1
  * add new PCI IDs in contrib:
    - xserver-xorg-video-intel 2:2.7.1-1
    - xserver-xorg-video-radeon 1:6.12.2-2
  * temporarily ship PCI IDs which were already removed from the corresponding
    xserver-xorg-video-* packages, conflict with older versions still providing
    them.
