fll-live-initscripts (3.0.23) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Kel Modderman ]
  * Implement script syntax/bashism sanity check at package build time,
    build-depend on devscripts and dash. Make failure to pass check fatal.
  * fll-xdm:
    - fix second syntax error from r17094, == was used, it is a bashism and
      fll-xdm is a dash script
    - overhaul logic behind setting default desktop display manager
  * fll-xorgconfig:
    - remove possible bashisms from script, making checkbashisms happy

  [ Stefan Lippers-Hollmann ]
  * catch script interpreters invoked with parameters as well.

