fll-live-initscripts (3.0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * distro-defaults:
    - override kdm and gdm LSB default start and stop values, so that they
      only start in runlevel 5, and stop in all other runlevels
    - manage the override with ucf, regenerate it every postinst with some
      careful sed
  * fll-live-initscripts:
    - reuse the function that distro-defaults uses to purge conffile from the
      disk and ucf database
    - update copyright year stamps in bin/fll_*
  * fll_analyze_initscripts:
    - remove the whitelist/blacklist input file cruft introduced with
      fll-build.bash developments

