fll-live-initscripts (2.0.26) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll_xorgconfig:
    - stop treating all ps/2 and USB mice as IMPS/@ protocol explicitly, this
      caused ExplorerPS/2 imput devices to go mad. Instead, attempt to allow
      xserver to do the right thing by using the auto protocal in all places
      we were hardcoding IMPS/2

