fll-live-initscripts (1.0.56) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll-hwsetup: depend on fll-locales to have already been started.
  * fll-locales: store all determined variables except for lang in
    /etc/defaul/fll-locales.
  * fll-locales.default: don't store default values here.

